<SYNC Start=2172628><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2176530><P Class=KRCC>
당신, 쯔보미씨와 육체관계를 맺고 있었지요?
<SYNC Start=2180611><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2183620><P Class=KRCC>
