<SYNC Start=2286676><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2287328><P Class=KRCC>
진정하세요
<SYNC Start=2288769><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2301790><P Class=KRCC>
